                <h4 class="my-4">Best Time to Visit</h4>
                <p>The ideal time to visit VGDS is between June and October, when dolphin sightings are most frequent. The sanctuary is accessible throughout the year.</p>
                <h4 class="my-4">Accessibility</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li><b>By Air:</b> The nearest airport is in Patna, approximately 235 kilometers from the sanctuary.</li>
                    <li><b>By Rail:</b> Bhagalpur Junction is the nearest railway station, about 15 kilometers from the sanctuary.</li>
                    <li><b>By Road:</b> The sanctuary is well-connected by road, with regular bus services from nearby towns and cities.</li>
